  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then they realized-- I don't know if they realized, or it was they just got bored with me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You'll never know what happens.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after a few threats, they let me go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went around the block to go home, still not knowing what went on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then I saw a group of school children being brought around the other corner into the street-- the teacher in front, the children two by two, and the teacher in the rear-- oh, I don't know, 40, 50 kids.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they were stopped in the middle of the block.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I hadn't even known that in the middle of the block was a-- a little synagogue, a temple, a shul, a beitstube.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They opened the doors and poured out the seats and pews and Torahs [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and set them on fire.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what they brought the children for, so the children could stand on the sidewalk and see that in the front yard of that building, religious objects were being burned.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I saw this, I turned the other corner around the block and ran home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I realized, this is major.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's why they thought, you know, information.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Obviously, this was not a-- a singular [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] accidental incident, because the school children were already paraded there before it really burned.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went home and asked my mother, please, close the door and don't go any place, and I'll stay here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and then later on, we had-- really, we didn't hear until evening, you know, that they had plundered and thrown in the windows and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
